<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.1">
<l>poṉṉiyaṟ kiṇkiṇi cuṭṭi puṟaṅkaṭṭit</l>
<l>taṉṉiya lōcai calaṟcala ṉeṉṟiṭa</l>
<l>miṉṉiyal mēkam viraintetir vantāṟpō</l>
<l>leṉṉiṭaik kōṭṭarā vaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vemperu māṉvārā vaccō vaccō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who came swiftly before me, having bound in place</l>
<l>the anklets and forehead ornament made of gold,</l>
<l>running to my waist like a cloud made of lightening</l>
<l>while the noise that is natural to that [anklet] made a tinkling sound,</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh! Oh! My Lord has come, Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
